    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You&nbsp; are&nbsp; skilled&nbsp; at&nbsp; shielding&nbsp; yourself&nbsp; from&nbsp; flames&nbsp; and&nbsp; magical effects.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n<p>Shield Focus, Shield Proficiency, base attack bonus +6.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong></p>\n<p>You&nbsp; gain&nbsp; the&nbsp; benefits&nbsp; of&nbsp; the&nbsp; rogue&rsquo;s&nbsp; evasion&nbsp; class ability as long as you have a heavy shield or tower shield in one hand. Unlike evasion, you do not need to be wearing light or medium armor to benefit from this effect.</p>",
